node.text: We’re hitting the road in the RV in just a couple weeks so I’ve started to plan our snacks and meals. The @gnclivewell TOTAL LEAN® LEAN SHAKE™ 25 and the @gnclivewell TOTAL LEAN® LAYERED PROTEIN BAR are on the list! They both come in Girl Scout inspired flavors and the lean shake is in a ready to drink bottle so I can quickly grab one for a tasty afternoon pick-me-up that will fuel my body. Don’t miss my Instagram story for my guilt free iced coffee recipe! #teamGNC #gnclivewell

node.text: #ad This week @gnclivewell is celebrating Women’s Health Week so I’m so excited to be sharing my prenatal and postpartum health and fitness tips with all my Momma’s out there. Comment below and let me know what being healthy means to you, and how you stayed active during your pregnancy! Also make sure to head over to @gnclivewell to check out my top product picks for Women’s Health Week! #gnclivewell #teamgnc

node.text: Officially back to working out and making videos for you guys. Honestly I just wasn’t ready to jump back in and wanted to take some extra time with the fam ❤️ here’s an awesome full arm workout! I did 4 sets of each exercise. First set 15 reps - second set 12 reps - 10 reps them finished with 8 on the last round

node.text: Hey friends!! We had an amazing trip to Disney! It’s been awhile here on my fitness page. I am gonna start posting workout videos again this week! 🙌🏻 I took a huge long break from the fitness stuff because I just wasn’t ready to jump back in yet. Thanks for sticking around! On another fun note Troy and I are gifting a family or couple or just some friends an all paid trip to Disneyland to stay at the grand Californian hotel($4000 value includes tickets flights etc) to enter just like/comment on this photo and then follow @troyleehunt & my other page @alexajeanbrown ❤️ we will post the winner on those pages

node.text:
Ahhhh I’m so excited to finally share with you that I got to partner with @gatorade zero 🙌🏻 To help promote their new protein drink, they asked me to create a week’s worth of workout’s that are now available to @samsclub members exclusively! As a mom of 4 kiddos, I know how hard it is finding time in the day to get a workout in, that’s why each of these workouts will take you no longer than 20 minutes and will cover all the muscle areas needed for a full body workout! 
 
The new @gatorade Zero Protein drink helps so much with recovery and helps replace what is lost during your sweaty workouts. It has 10g of protein, zero sugar, sodium and potassium. You can now get a variety pack at your local @samsclub
 
#GZeroProteinWorkouts #SamsClub #Partner

node.text: We’re hitting the road in the RV in just a couple weeks so I’ve started to plan our snacks and meals. The @gnclivewell TOTAL LEAN® LEAN SHAKE™ 25 and the @gnclivewell TOTAL LEAN® LAYERED PROTEIN BAR are on the list! They both come in Girl Scout inspired flavors and the lean shake is in a ready to drink bottle so I can quickly grab one for a tasty afternoon pick-me-up that will fuel my body. Don’t miss my Instagram story for my guilt free iced coffee recipe! #teamGNC #gnclivewell

node.text: #ad I can’t believe I’m already 30 weeks pregnant!! Anyone else been here since Logan was a baby? Okay, we all know that taking prenatal vitamins is super important during pregnancy. I want to make sure me and the baby are as healthy as possible and ready to take on this crazy year! Vitamins in general are just amazing to take. That’s why I also got the family some @gnclivewell vitamins as well. They have these amazing gummy ones that the kiddos LOVE taking and there's even some options for Troy as well. What are some ways you get the whole family involved with staying healthy during this crazy time?! Comment below and let me know! #TeamGNC #MultisForTheFamily
